{"tid":1353013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[[[[[集中討論區]]]]]一定要入元朗","createTime":"2019-07-23T01:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T01:47:09.000Z","uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3464e757995a54f86bf93091464afa11fdf1d9ac","tid":1353013,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:24:01.000Z","msg":"各位巴打,我知上環單野緊要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過拜託咪撚借位貼其他野</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1.無差別攻擊孕婦,記者,女人,黑衫以外人士<br />\n2.追上車打其他唔相關既市民<br />\n3.廢鐵唔開車,唔關門,引致白衣人可以追上車<br />\n4.警察失去其作用,刑事暴力案,竟然係消防救護比警察早到<br />\n5.光頭白衫警兇記者,同鄉黑搭膊頭<br />\n6.防暴警長時間企係一群手持武器既白衫鄉黑前面,指揮官話一個都見唔到<br />\n7.淨係西鐵站都有3,40人,求其拉6個,仲要未有起訴<br />\n留意返,荃灣炸藥單野即日起訴,提堂一條龍<br />\n8.立法會議員何君堯事前向暴徙打氣振奮<br />\n數漏左再補<br />\n<br />\n各位男人,各位香港人,忍撚完未?<br />\n各位勇武巴打,營養不良既差仔唔需要驚佢地<br />\n由呢個post開始集中討論"},{"pid":"be31707ca11bedf9a8ad3c1d2325ee640078ea85","tid":1353013,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我自己推得啦,各位巴打留言就唔好推,集中討論點樣做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac5a183c3278fb9e8cc36d7a2bc94bfbab6fd2a","tid":1353013,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:25:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b617015892a4cfa4f783d2069f57851e147af4d","tid":1353013,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:25:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6977ee16381907b6b5206d6f46fbadc4f2173b6b","tid":1353013,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:25:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ac6a45f668cd95dd90e6df4e15157e770260e3","tid":1353013,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB